{"tid":1564702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post係睇完得個知字，所以引唔到人回覆；引箭或具爭議嘅post，就多人討論易上熱門","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:49:53.000Z","uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"061384ada51df59abfde8b7491a3faafa8b401af","tid":1564702,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"熱門其實好多膠post、令人屌出聲新聞post、打飛機post、嗌交post、陰謀論post<br />\n因為呢堆野最吸引到人傾<br />\n一傾可能回五六個comment<br />\n<br />\n至於行動post <br />\n睇完都係得個知字<br />\n已經唔係好吸引到人留言<br />\n你好心推post<br />\n寫個推字<br />\n都係得一個comment<br />\n<br />\npost 嘅唔同性質<br />\n註定左佢地嘅命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登冇機制推行動post<br />\n大家唯有靠自己<br />\n見到支持嘅行動post<br />\n冇野講都入去推五六次<br />\n先抗衡到其他post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdaa005b25a1ba271a151ea6a93ffa5d42f8c3b","tid":1564702,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:16:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2b3e33a691ad4054b62bb08214078a05bbcf7195","tid":1564702,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:17:29.000Z","msg":"[國際民主日遊行攻略] 915 去港島遊行定入商場？溝埋做瀨尿牛丸咪得囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563777\